Dr asked me to give blood test ie tsh, hba1c, vit d , HIV in this clinic only . They told once the reports are ready , you will get a call from clinic regarding the tests given . I got a call from clinic after a day , saying that everything in reports are fine only sugar is bit high so avoid any sugary foods that’s it . I asked them to send the reports by any means either by WhatsApp or email . They told will send in 5 mins but they never sent at all . I kept on calling but no one sent them . I had appointment with dr after two weeks . When I went that time they had kept the reports in my file only after two weeks of giving my blood test . Then seeing reports the dr tells me that my thyroid is HIGH , VITAMIN D IS VERY LOW and HBA1C is slightly elevated. So immediately start with thyroid tablets , vit d and come back after a week for a scan . **** *** *** ***** ********** **** ** ** ***** ****  *** ***** ** **** *** *** ******* ********** **** ***** ** **** * 
I came back after a week for a scan. Scan was done and they told heartbeat is very less and be ready for anything to happen , and we’ll wait for a week for another scan . The dr didn’t give any hope but told we might have to abort if we didn’t hear any heart beat in next week . After a week , the heartbeat was completely stopped and she told that we have to abort it immediately. Gave medications , I started bleeding heavy and after two weeks came back and scanned for remains . There was a less than 1 cm remains in the cervix. Dr. Apoorva Pallam Reddy asked me to do D&E ( which costs ₹.35000) immediately and she asked me start to prep for the surgery on the same day . I trusted her and got done D&E .

This time when we went to Dr, she didn’t ask me take any other blood test other than beta Hcg . **** *** *** ****** ********** ** **** * She put me on blood thinner injections which I have to put every day where single injections they prescribe cost ₹425 . Along with lot other ,only medications which will cost you per day ₹250 . (₹.675 per day * 8 weeks ) . This time for up to 8 weeks of my pregnancy I was taking all these meds and inj daily, but after 8 weeks scan the dr said that my pregnancy was a blighted ovum and we should immediately abort . But this time she said we have to do a D&E SURGERY ITSELF DIRECTLY AND SEND THE PRODUCTS FOR GENETICAL TESTING WHICH WILL COST ME 35000 for D&E AND 18000 for GENETIC TESTING .
